Third-party attribution
=======================

This project is inspired by and uses dimensions from:

- "Cisco AIR-AP-BRACKET-1" by nicba1010
- Thingiverse: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:5491712
- Source file referenced locally as AIR-AP-BRACKET-1.scad
- Repo copy: third_party/thingiverse-5491712/AIR-AP-BRACKET-1.scad
- License: BSD license, as stated by the source model

The original AIR-AP-BRACKET-1.scad dimensions used here include the four Cisco AP
slider/keyhole cutouts and recessed two-layer slider-hole behavior. This project
changes the surrounding bracket shape, ventilation pattern, and HomeRacker
mounting interface.
